# Empty & error states

Every user-facing flow needs:

| State | Requirement |
|-------|-------------|
| Loading | Visible feedback (spinner or label) |
| Error | Message + recovery action (retry, go back, contact recruiter) |
| Empty | Explain why empty + what to do next |

Examples: admin table (“Create an intake link above”), invalid invite (“Ask your recruiter”), parse failure (stay on upload + manual continue).

Do not leave blank sections with no guidance.
